{
  "texts": [
    "Their main goal is to maintain their status in the populace by averting any noteworthy alterations.",
    "Members of this group, or search agents, are ranked in the middle and are essential in exploiting the variations in the share percentages of the initial group members.",
    "In optimization situations, it is their responsibility to find the optimal location.",
    "Usually, this group makes about 26-50% of the search space.",
    "It takes at least two people to compare the targets of the members of the first group in a meaningful way."
  ]
}